<div id="review_3231531716" class="review" itemprop="reviews" itemscope itemtype="http://schema.org/Review">
  <link itemprop="url" href="https://www.goodreads.com/review/show/3231531716" />
    <a title="Cat on the Mat" class="left imgcol" href="/user/show/111400475-cat-on-the-mat"><img alt="Cat on the Mat" src="https://images.gr-assets.com/users/1584258915p2/111400475.jpg" /></a>

  <div class="left bodycol">
    <div class="reviewHeader uitext stacked">
        <a class="reviewDate createdAt right" href="/review/show/3231531716?book_show_action=true">Mar 15, 2020</a>

      <span itemprop="author" itemscope itemtype="http://schema.org/Person">
        <a title="Cat on the Mat" class="user" itemprop="url" name="Cat on the Mat" href="/user/show/111400475-cat-on-the-mat">Cat on the Mat</a>
      </span>

        rated it
        <span class=" staticStars notranslate" title="really liked it"><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10">really liked it</span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p0"></span></span>



        

    </div>


        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer3231531716" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer10894547536069338613">I really enjoyed reading this book because it truly made me think and reflect how or why any woman would or could stay with a cheating husband. This story looks into the way these women were raised from childhood and offers alternative reasoning that could lie behind their future decisions. The author has obviously done thorough research on these women and their lives which made it a very informative read for me. I would definitely recommend this book to anyone who has even a passing curiosity i</span>
  <span id="freeText10894547536069338613" style="display:none">I really enjoyed reading this book because it truly made me think and reflect how or why any woman would or could stay with a cheating husband. This story looks into the way these women were raised from childhood and offers alternative reasoning that could lie behind their future decisions. The author has obviously done thorough research on these women and their lives which made it a very informative read for me. I would definitely recommend this book to anyone who has even a passing curiosity into the psychology behind the complex lives of these iconic women, and I have already recommended it to my friends.</span>
  <a data-text-id="10894547536069338613" href="#" onclick="swapContent($(this));; return false;">...more</a>

          </span>
        </div>


